Class RabbitsGrassSimulationModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • SimModelImpl
      • RabbitsGrassSimulationModel

  • public class RabbitsGrassSimulationModel
extends SimModelImpl
    Class that implements the simulation model for the rabbits grass simulation. This is the first class which needs to be setup in order to run Repast simulation. It manages the entire RePast environment and the simulation.
